data.description: This meticulously kept single-story home offers 2,450 sq.ft. of living space on an 11,016 sq.ft. lot with only one immediate neighbor. Impeccable curb appeal and a charming front entrance greet you upon arrival. The floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, family room, dining area, and kitchen for relaxation and entertaining. The kitchen, with its breakfast bar and eat-in area, inspires culinary creativity. Patio door opens to an attached deck and expansive backyard, perfect for outdoor gatherings. The primary suite features a bay window seat, outdoor access, and a spa-like en-suite bathroom. Two additional bedrooms and a well-appointed guest bathroom provide comfort for guests. The backyard offers privacy and room for outdoor activities. Located in a coveted golf community, this home provides access to amenities like golf courses, clubhouses, and tennis courts. Experience luxury living and pride of ownership in this rare gem of a home.
